## Cookie Lifecycle

```text
User Visits Website
        ↓
Server Sends Set-Cookie Header
        ↓
Browser Stores Cookie
        ↓
User Visits Another Page
        ↓
Browser Sends Cookie Header
        ↓
Server Identifies User
```

