## Viewing Cookies in Browser

Modern browsers allow users to inspect cookies through Developer Tools.

### Steps

1. Open Developer Tools

```text
F12
```

or

```text
Right Click → Inspect
```

---

### Navigate to Network Tab

```text
Developer Tools
      ↓
Network Tab
```

This displays all requests made by the browser.

---

### Inspect a Request

Select any request and view:

```text
Headers
Cookies
Response
```

---

### Cookie Information

You can see:

```text
Cookie Name
Cookie Value
Expiration Date
Domain
Path
```

